bill-collectors move in.

797
00:51:57,489 --> 00:52:00,538
You sound sweet,
but you don't make sense.

798
00:52:06,582 --> 00:52:08,416
The inn is so romantic looking.

799
00:52:08,417 --> 00:52:11,511
