me in on your secret?

843
00:56:35,851 --> 00:56:37,101
Oh, it's no secret.

844
00:56:37,102 --> 00:56:39,228
Ted Hanover is looking for
a new dancing partner

845
00:56:39,229 --> 00:56:40,479
and we've decided
to give you the job.

846
