01:30:25,420 --> 01:30:28,380
Oh, sure, women has to be
told things the right way.

1295
01:30:28,381 --> 01:30:30,053
Yes, sir!

1296
01:30:42,604 --> 01:30:46,565
At last, the night I've been
dreaming about actually here.

