01:35:22,759 --> 01:35:26,178
Come on, everybody, let's get
settled now. This is the picture.

1389
01:35:28,097 --> 01:35:29,689
Hit the snow!

1390
01:35:31,809 --> 01:35:33,606
All right, roll 'em!

1391
01:35:39,609 --> 01:35:41,652
Sorry, Mr. Hanover,
but when the red light's on

